Andre PICKETT NO. 2018-KH-0508 Supreme Court of Louisiana. May 11, 2018

WRIT NOT CONSIDERED. Petitioner has not demonstrated that he sought review in the court(s) below before filing in this Court nor shown the "extraordinary circumstances" that would justify bypassing *1011that level of review. La.S.Ct.R. X § 5(b).
